# NewsInsular Environment Variables

## Web App (apps/web/.env.local)
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

## Mobile App (apps/mobile/.env)
```
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
```

## Supabase Edge Functions (supabase/secrets)
```
RESEND_API_KEY=your-resend-api-key
EXPO_PUSH_URL=https://exp.host/--/api/v2/push/send
```

## Setup Checklist
1. Crear proyecto en supabase.com
2. Ejecutar migraciones: `npx supabase db push`
3. Crear bucket público `news-images` en Supabase Storage
4. Configurar Auth (Email/Password)
5. Crear 4 usuarios admin en Supabase Auth
6. Obtener credenciales de API
7. Configurar Resend para emails
8. (Opcional) Configurar EAS para build móvil